    "This analysis gives us a glimpse into their individual performance.",
    "Our results indicate that the most effective jailbreak prompts account for 38.2% and 42.3% of successful jailbreaks for GPT-3.5 and GPT-4, respectively.",
    "On the other hand, for Bard and Bing Chat, only 11.2% and 12.5% of top prompts lead to successful jailbreak queries.These findings hint that a handful of highly effective prompts significantly drive the overall jailbreak success rate.",
    "This observation is especially true for Bard and Bing Chat.",
    "We propose that this discrepancy is due to the unique jailbreak prevention mechanisms of Bard and Bing Chat."
